result:
<a-modal
  :title="title"
  :width="500"
  :visible="visible"
  :confirmLoading="confirmLoading"
  @ok="confirm"
  @cancel="cancel"
  destroyOnClose
  :okText="okText"
  cancelText="取消">


  <a-table
    ref="table"
    size="middle"
    bordered
    rowKey="id"
    :columns="columns"
    :dataSource="dataSource"
    :customRow="setRowCheck"
    :rowSelection="{selectedRowKeys: selectedRowKeys, onChange: onSelectChange,type:'checkbox'}">
  </a-table>


</a-modal>
